<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" ?>
<Defs>

    <TraitDef>
		<defName>BA_Trait_Student_Valkyrie</defName>
		<ignoreConfigErrors>true</ignoreConfigErrors>
		<commonality>0.0</commonality>
		<degreeDatas>
			<li>
				<label>瓦尔基里警察学校学生</label>
				<description>{PAWN_nameDef}是瓦尔基里警察学校的学生。</description>
				<statOffsets>
					<MoveSpeed>1.0</MoveSpeed>
					<HuntingStealth>0.5</HuntingStealth>
				</statOffsets>
				<skillGains>
					<Shooting>4</Shooting>
				</skillGains>
			</li>
		</degreeDatas>
	</TraitDef>

    <TraitDef>
		<ignoreConfigErrors>true</ignoreConfigErrors>
		<commonality>0.0</commonality>
		<defName>BA_Trait_Kanna</defName>
		<degreeDatas>
			<li>
				<label>狂犬</label>
				<description>" 在确定的犯罪面前，康娜的字典中没有「放弃」一词，她这样的执拗深入人心。\n为了查明真相被世人冠上了「狂犬」这一绰号，并广泛地被人知晓。\n（其实这也和她平时总是臭着一张脸有关）"</description>
				<statOffsets>
					<SocialImpact>-0.12</SocialImpact>
					<WorkSpeedGlobal>0.25</WorkSpeedGlobal>
					<AimingDelayFactor>-0.25</AimingDelayFactor>
					<ShootingAccuracyPawn>0.25</ShootingAccuracyPawn>
                    <MeleeDodgeChance>0.25</MeleeDodgeChance>
					<PainShockThreshold>-1</PainShockThreshold>
				</statOffsets>
				<statFactors>
					<IncomingDamageFactor>0.6</IncomingDamageFactor>
                    <ArrestSuccessChance>3</ArrestSuccessChance>
				</statFactors>
			</li>
		</degreeDatas>
        <modExtensions>
			<li Class="AKE_OperatorExtension.DefExt_SkillLossRate">
				<skillLossFactor>0.5</skillLossFactor>
			</li>
		</modExtensions>
	</TraitDef>

    <TraitDef>
		<ignoreConfigErrors>true</ignoreConfigErrors>
		<commonality>0.0</commonality>
		<defName>BA_Trait_Fubuki</defName>
		<degreeDatas>
			<li>
				<label>懒鬼警员</label>
				<description>吹雪平时总是享受着不思进取的窗边族生活，对于工作什么的总是能应付就应付。不过吹雪其实很有能力，从她总是能想出办法偷懒和糊弄工作上就能看出来。而且在面对真正重要的事情时，她也会以悠闲的样子负起责任。</description>
				<statOffsets>
					<SocialImpact>0.18</SocialImpact>
					<WorkSpeedGlobal>-0.4</WorkSpeedGlobal>
					<MentalBreakThreshold>-0.12</MentalBreakThreshold>
					<RestRateMultiplier>-0.15</RestRateMultiplier>
				</statOffsets>
                <disallowedMentalStates>
                    <li>InsultingSpree</li>
                    <li>TargetedInsultingSpree</li>
                </disallowedMentalStates>
			</li>
		</degreeDatas>
	</TraitDef>

    <TraitDef>
		<ignoreConfigErrors>true</ignoreConfigErrors>
		<commonality>0.0</commonality>
		<defName>BA_Trait_Kirino</defName>
		<degreeDatas>
			<li>
				<label>热血警员</label>
				<description>桐乃总是憧憬着前辈警员的英姿，因此她努力学习着各种警备有关的知识并且尽自己最大的热情完成巡逻任务，不过却总是因为热血上头说错话或没有很好的思考而犯错。</description>
				<statOffsets>
					<SocialImpact>-0.06</SocialImpact>
					<WorkSpeedGlobal>0.2</WorkSpeedGlobal>
					<MentalBreakThreshold>-0.12</MentalBreakThreshold>
					<RestRateMultiplier>0.3</RestRateMultiplier>
				</statOffsets>
                <disallowedMentalStates>
                    <li>InsultingSpree</li>
                    <li>TargetedInsultingSpree</li>
                </disallowedMentalStates>
                <statFactors>
                    <ArrestSuccessChance>0.5</ArrestSuccessChance>
				</statFactors>
			</li>
		</degreeDatas>
	</TraitDef>

</Defs>